                        li
                            a(href="https://github.com/siyuan-note/siyuan-ios" class="download__link" target="_blank") iOS App
                        li
                            a(href="https://github.com/siyuan-note/siyuan-chrome" class="download__link" target="_blank") Chrome Clipping Extension
                div(class="item")
                    h3 Do I need to pay to use it?
                    p Local functions are completely free to use, cloud services require&nbsp;
